OOC: Will someone respond to the Destrons?  We came to the Blackfortress, to 
discuss an alliance, but no one is listening.

:::Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian:::

::Starscream's jaw drops.  he rubs his eyes to make sure he isnt dreaming.  
Bludgeon and Obsidian are just as amazed::
Starscream: KITKAT?! HOW?
Bludgeon: how is the question. Ive seen people come back form the dead 
before, but i didnt think it would be possible here.
Obsidian: Quit questioning Bludgeon, the point is, our Kitkat has returned!
::Starscream follows Drillbit::
Starscream: What is it you want to talk with about? And.... how?

--part1_8b.3f842d8.27e9f8e7_boundary
